high_descs: Turn around and walk to the opposite side of the counter island.
Pick up a potato from the counter.
Go stand in front of the toaster.
Open the leftmost upper cabinet and put the potato in the bowl.
Pick up the bowl with the potato.
Turn left and face the microwave.
Put the bowl and potato into the microwave and cook the potato.
anns.task_desc: Microwave a potato in a bowl.

high_descs: Turn around, turn left towards the white door, make a left turn and go to the black stools near the counter top.
Pick up the potato on top of the counter top.
Walk slightly to the left, go to the counter top with a toaster on top of it and face the cabinet on top of the toaster.
Open the cabinet's door and put the potato inside a clear bowl.
Grab the bowl with the potato in it and close the cabinet's door.
Go to the left to the microwave on top of the counter top.
Open the microwave, put the bowl in the microwave and cook the potato.
anns.task_desc: Cook a bowl with a potato in it using the microwave.

high_descs: Walk around the island to the side with the stools.
Pick up the potato behind the salt on the counter.
Take the potato to the counter next to the toaster.
Open the cabinet above and to the left of the toaster, put the potato in the bowl.
Take the bowl with the potato in it out of the cabinet.
Walk over to the microwave across the room.
Put the bowl with a potato in it inside the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a potato inside of it into the microwave.

high_descs: Turn right, hang a left around the end of the counter, turn left at the door and face the two black stools on your left.
Pick up the potato behind the salt shaker on the counter.
Turn left, hang a right at the door and head across the room to the toaster on the counter.
Place the potato inside the upper left cabinet above the spoon into the clear bowl.
Pick up the clear bowl with the potato inside.
Turn left to face the microwave.
Put the bowl with the potato to the left of the mug inside the microwave and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place a bowl with a potato in a microwave.
